<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!--
/Library/LaunchDaemons/com.whoeverwants.colima-watchdog.plist on the Mac mini.

System LaunchDaemon that runs colima-watchdog.sh every 60s AS the devbox owner
(UserName=sccarey) so `colima`/`docker` resolve the user's VM state (which lives
under /Users/sccarey/.colima). Runs from boot regardless of GUI login. The
VM-level analog of com.whoeverwants.caddy-watchdog.plist — caddy-watchdog keeps
the host Caddy up, this keeps the devbox VM (Caddy's upstream) up.

Install (ONE-TIME, on the Mac host itself — colima is a host process and is NOT
reachable via the in-VM cmd-api, so this cannot be deployed from the sandbox /
remote-mac.sh):
  sudo cp scripts/mac-mini/colima-watchdog.sh /usr/local/bin/colima-watchdog.sh
  sudo chmod 755 /usr/local/bin/colima-watchdog.sh
  sudo cp scripts/mac-mini/com.whoeverwants.colima-watchdog.plist /Library/LaunchDaemons/
  sudo chown root:wheel /Library/LaunchDaemons/com.whoeverwants.colima-watchdog.plist
  sudo chmod 644       /Library/LaunchDaemons/com.whoeverwants.colima-watchdog.plist
  sudo launchctl bootstrap system /Library/LaunchDaemons/com.whoeverwants.colima-watchdog.plist
  sudo launchctl kickstart -k system/com.whoeverwants.colima-watchdog

If Virtualization.framework ever refuses to boot the VM headless under a
LaunchDaemon, install instead as a per-user LaunchAgent in
~/Library/LaunchAgents/ (drop the <UserName> key, `launchctl bootstrap
gui/$(id -u)`) so it runs inside the owner's login session.

The DOCTYPE line is intentionally omitted — modern macOS accepts a plist with
just the XML preamble + <plist version="1.0">, and the DOCTYPE URL gets mangled
by chat-client autolink wrapping when pasted through a heredoc.
-->
<plist version="1.0">
<dict>
    <key>Label</key>
    <string>com.whoeverwants.colima-watchdog</string>

    <key>UserName</key>
    <string>sccarey</string>

    <key>EnvironmentVariables</key>
    <dict>
        <key>HOME</key>
        <string>/Users/sccarey</string>
        <key>PATH</key>
        <string>/opt/homebrew/bin:/usr/local/bin:/usr/bin:/bin:/usr/sbin:/sbin</string>
    </dict>

    <key>ProgramArguments</key>
    <array>
        <string>/usr/local/bin/colima-watchdog.sh</string>
    </array>

    <key>StartInterval</key>
    <integer>60</integer>

    <key>RunAtLoad</key>
    <true/>

    <key>StandardOutPath</key>
    <string>/Users/sccarey/Library/Logs/colima-watchdog.out.log</string>

    <key>StandardErrorPath</key>
    <string>/Users/sccarey/Library/Logs/colima-watchdog.err.log</string>
</dict>
</plist>
